Package: cockpit-authelia-users
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, cockpit (>= 276), python3-yaml, python3-argon2
Description: Cockpit plugin for Authelia user management
 A web-based user management interface for Authelia that provides:
  - List, create, edit, and delete Authelia users
  - Manage user groups and permissions
  - Password management with Argon2id hashing
  - Modern React-based UI with PatternFly components
 .
 This package provides a user-friendly interface for managing
 Authelia users through Cockpit's web interface.
